has higher functions.

04:17.413 --> 04:19.409
Would you like me to show you
how your stunt

04:19.410 --> 04:20.349
with Troy and Britta
will play itself out?

04:20.350 --> 04:21.983
Why not?

04:21.985 --> 04:23.852
Execute simulation Troy/Britta.

04:23.853 --> 04:27.621
