the same table.

04:43.871 --> 04:45.906
So I guess Annie's pretty hot
to get us together.

04:45.907 --> 04:48.875
She probably just doesn't
understand people.

04:48.876 --> 04:50.310
Well, the sooner
the food comes,

04:50.311 --> 04:52.478
