08:04.731 --> 08:06.598
and you're a hotshot
upstart administrator,

08:06.599 --> 08:08.167
but damn the rules,
damn the system,

08:08.168 --> 08:10.870
damn our two foot height
disparity, I want you.

08:10.871 --> 08:14.306
Okay, Abed, I get it, we have
different sensibilities.

08:14.307 --> 08:16.241
