12:49.697 --> 12:53.234
Abed Nadir,
psychiatric patient 1373,

12:53.235 --> 12:55.336
control freak with no empathy.

12:55.337 --> 12:58.972
People bend over backwards
to cater to him.

12:58.973 --> 13:03.443
